casebody.data:
Ali ABDI and Emamian Abdi, Plaintiffs,
v.
Joseph LOONAM and Danielle Loonam, Defendants. Joseph Loonam and Danielle Loonam, Plaintiffs-Movants,
v.
Ali Abdi and Emamian Abdi a/k/a Effat S. Emamian, Defendants. M-841 September Term 2018
080714 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 3, 2019

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for counsel fees and costs is granted, in part. Counsel fees are awarded in the amount of $ 1,380.00, and costs are awarded in the amount of $ 73.80 for a total award of $ 1,453.80.
